---
title: Herby Beef Sandwiches and Cranberry Sauce with Potato Wedges and Zesty Mayo Dip
description: Reminiscent of your favourite holiday feast, stuffing-inspired garlic toasts, sweet cranberry sauce and herbed beef patties come together in this delectable sandwich. Grainy mustard-mayo adds zest, both in the sandwich and as a dipper for the potato wedges.
